Revision history for App-QuestionValidator

0.02    19 Jan 2013
        - This version should be compatible with Perl 5.12.*
        - Most errors should have the offending line pointed out
          correctly now.
        - Text::CSV errors should be printed using the same syntax as
          the rest of the errors.
        - Can handle multiple questions from STDIN, and multiple
          questions from one file.

0.01    05 Jan 2013
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

